FSV GTK3 Migration Plan
========================

**Initial version:** 2.0.0
**Versioning scheme:** 2.{phase}.{item} (e.g., Phase 2, Item 3 = 2.2.03)

> After each phase is complete, the user should build, run, and test the
> application before proceeding to the next phase.


Goal: Migrate from GTK+ 2.0 to GTK 3, with pragmatic middle-of-the-road
library choices. Each step should leave the code compilable and runnable.


